title: One Bedroom with Vaulted Ceilings
posting_body: ['This lovely community is centrally located in Renton to provide easy access to both work and play throughout the city and surrounding area.', 'Each exquisite home offers modern fixtures and fine finishes to fit every individual lifestyle, while still accommodating the ease of adding your own personal touches throughout your new home.', 'You’ll find a wonderful array of amenities including 9 ft elevated ceilings, cozy living room fireplaces, and a fitness studio.', '-Modern Studio, 1 & 2 Bedroom Floorplans', '-High Speed Internet included in Media Package', '-select locations only, ask for details', '-BBQ Grilling Stations', '-Surrounded by Gourmet Restaurants & Sophisticated Shops', '-Limited Access Entry', '-Grand 9ft and Vaulted Ceilings', '-Updated Stainless Steel Appliances', '-Downtown Renton Views', '-Large', 'Dual-Pane Windows with Blinds', '-Upgraded Features & Finishes', '-Easy Access to I-5, WA-167 & Public Transportation', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Prices and Availability are Subject to Change Without Notice']
